snippet.title: Brick Breaker Premium
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/874780

The classic arcade brick-breaker game.

It's Back!

You are the hero “Blippy” the paddle, that has to save planet Earth from it's greatest threat. Can you finish the game and save Earth from “The Evil Snarfer”?...

- 35 Challenging Levels to Complete.
- Heroic Storyline, Where It All Began!
- Classic Power-ups.
- See Ending Cutscenes If You Can Complete The Game!!!

It's Addictive and Loads of Fun! Good Luck!
